description: Available NOW Gorgeous newly built (2017) condo offers high end finishes, hardwoods Central A/C, in-unit laundry, and1 HEATED garage parking spot. Open living & dining area with gas fireplace provides a perfect space for entertaining. The modern kitchen features ample custom cabinetry, Bertazzoni range, microwave drawer and huge peninsula with seating for 4+. The spacious master bedroom is complete with large built-out closet, a beautiful marble bath, and deluxe fixtures. Rent includes high speed WiFi & water/sewer. The unit is centrally located and provides direct access to the best of Southie hot spots, restaurants, shops, & Broadway Station.
